= MODULE

sysctl 

= DESCRIPTION

This is the sysctl module.
Configure and manage sysctl

== Supported Platforms

* Debian
* Redhat and others: not  tested yet)

== Main classes

* sysctl($arg) :: Install and configure sysctl

== Sample Usage

     import sysctl
     [...]
     class { 'sysctl':
           arg => 'val'
     }

